#

Crispy Herb-Crusted Salmon with Lemon-Dill Sauce and Asparagus

$25.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleoLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyElegant

Description

A delightful and elegant dish featuring crispy salmon, complemented by a zesty lemon-dill sauce and tender asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 pieces
  • Panko breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lemon zest: 1 tablespoon
  • Garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Dijon mustard: 1 tablespoon
  • Asparagus: 1 pound
